                    <h3>Advanced</h3>
                    <p>In addition to all Standard level functions, the new Advanced level includes more other functions, e.g.: performance that is superior to Basic or Standard level caches, bigger workloads, disaster recovery and enhanced safety. Other functions include:</p>
                    <ul class="ul-price-style ">
                        <li><a id="" target="_blank" href="">Redis Retention</a> allows you to save data stored in the Redis Cache. You can also obtain screenshots and back up data, so as to upload them in case of failure.</li>
                        <li><a id="" target="_blank" href="">Redis Cluster</a> automatically segments data in multiple Redis nodes, thus you can create workloads (bigger than 53 GB) with bigger memory size and obtain better performance.</li>
                        <li><a id="home_redia_network" target="_blank" href="/home/features/virtual-network/">Azure Virtual Network (VNet)</a> is deployed to provide enhanced safety for Azure Redis Cache, and also offer subnet and access control policies and further limit other access functions.</li>
                    </ul>
